text: Motion

Hello, I am Hana Suzuki
── and this is Haruki-chan

Fufuu～...!
Hello～
Motion

Waaaa!
There're so many people watching～

Ahah, amazing! Even though it was an 
impromptu stream. Thank you!
So what is everyone up toー?

We're about to have a dance lesson, but since we still
have some free time, we decided to stream a bitー
Yeah...!
Ah,  someone said "I'm watching this will eating some Taiyaki."

Ahah, taiyaki sounds nice.
Want to go buy some together later, Haruki?
Fufu, certainly.
Motion

Ah, taiyaki with sweet rice dumplings inside...?
That sounds delicious, doesn't it～!
Eh?
That was a comment just now...!

Eeeh, that's definitely tasty──!
Even though we're about to have a lesson, I'm so hungry now...
Right～...
Motion

── "Is this a taiyaki stream?"
Ah s-sorry!
A taiyaki stream? Of course not...!

We were planning to use this stream to show our resolve to
to do our best in todays lesson～...!

We'll work hard so that we can show you all
the fruits of our efforts as soon as possible!
Let's do our beeest!
